WEBVTT

02:17.000 --> 02:17.730
How could you

02:18.310 --> 02:19.560
just forget about me?

02:30.680 --> 02:31.630
I want to see

02:32.120 --> 02:32.920
where exactly

02:33.310 --> 02:34.360
you are injured.

02:58.800 --> 02:59.860
What are you doing?

03:08.360 --> 03:08.760
You...

03:10.000 --> 03:11.800
You just said you had a headache.

03:12.000 --> 03:13.120
Why are you here?

03:16.240 --> 03:17.640
You got drunk last night,

03:17.960 --> 03:18.710
so

03:19.190 --> 03:20.240
I sent you back.

03:21.870 --> 03:23.240
I was afraid you would feel unwell,

03:23.240 --> 03:23.590
so...

03:24.079 --> 03:25.410
so I stayed by your side.

03:27.800 --> 03:29.470
You stayed with me all night?

03:35.280 --> 03:36.680
If there's nothing else,

03:37.240 --> 03:38.240
I'll leave first.

03:38.590 --> 03:38.990
You...

03:39.120 --> 03:40.750
keep sleeping. Go ahead.

04:02.870 --> 04:04.870
How did I get drunk again yesterday?

04:06.870 --> 04:08.150
Yesterday,

04:08.870 --> 04:10.600
there was some kind of banquet.

04:14.750 --> 04:17.550
It seems they said
Xiao Chi is going to the capital.

04:18.600 --> 04:19.630
So it seems

04:20.269 --> 04:22.070
we have no choice but to obey
the decree and return to the capital.

04:22.070 --> 04:22.920
For now,

04:23.360 --> 04:24.760
Her Highness seems fine,

04:25.000 --> 04:27.480
but the female official
with her knows martial arts.

04:27.480 --> 04:29.190
Is she going back to the capital with us?

04:29.190 --> 04:30.390
There's no other way.

04:30.480 --> 04:31.940
If we don't let her follow,

04:32.040 --> 04:34.300
Her Highness will surely be displeased.

04:34.390 --> 04:35.270
General Xiao.

04:41.390 --> 04:43.120
If you have something to discuss,

04:43.120 --> 04:44.320
I'll come back later.

04:44.430 --> 04:45.030
It's fine.

04:46.040 --> 04:47.750
Physician Han,
if you have something to say,

04:47.750 --> 04:48.480
just say it.

04:51.430 --> 04:51.920
Oh.

04:52.600 --> 04:53.860
Then I'll go out first.

04:55.310 --> 04:56.070
No need.

04:57.040 --> 04:57.840
You guys talk.

05:15.600 --> 05:17.600
I heard you are going to the capital.

05:18.120 --> 05:18.720
Yes.

05:19.950 --> 05:21.080
When will you leave?

05:22.270 --> 05:23.120
In 3 days.

05:23.950 --> 05:24.720
Then...

05:25.750 --> 05:27.390
Then what if you get sick?

05:28.270 --> 05:29.200
Military orders

05:29.480 --> 05:30.340
must be obeyed.

05:36.920 --> 05:39.270
But with your treatment during this time,

05:39.920 --> 05:40.870
I'm much better now.

05:40.870 --> 05:41.720
But I...

05:44.870 --> 05:46.190
If the treatment is interrupted

05:46.190 --> 05:49.120
and the illness recurs,
the condition will grow far worse.

05:49.120 --> 05:50.560
There's not much time left.

05:50.560 --> 05:52.159
I can't worry about that much.

05:52.159 --> 05:52.600
I...

05:54.720 --> 05:55.580
Physician Han,

05:55.950 --> 05:56.830
after I leave,

05:58.070 --> 05:59.200
what are your plans?

05:59.510 --> 06:00.370
Once you leave,

06:00.480 --> 06:02.880
what's the point of
my staying in this city?

06:03.000 --> 06:04.460
I'm going back to Changmo.

06:11.240 --> 06:11.680
Okay.

06:12.600 --> 06:13.330
At that time,

06:13.680 --> 06:15.510
I will have someone
prepare your medical fees

06:15.510 --> 06:16.710
and more gifts for you

06:17.000 --> 06:17.750
to take back.

06:17.750 --> 06:18.950
Who needs your gifts?

06:24.480 --> 06:27.310
Tonight, I will give you
acupuncture for the last time,

06:27.310 --> 06:28.830
then you go back to the capital,

06:28.830 --> 06:30.360
and I'll go back to Changmo.

06:37.510 --> 06:38.440
Seven years ago,

06:38.600 --> 06:39.800
you came here with me,

06:40.390 --> 06:42.590
leaving our homes and families behind,

06:43.159 --> 06:45.560
shedding our blood outside Tianlang Pass,

06:45.600 --> 06:46.860
because Tianlang Pass

06:47.070 --> 06:49.000
is the most important place in Jinglan.

06:49.000 --> 06:50.870
Behind us are our families

06:51.720 --> 06:53.510
and the thousands of citizens of Jinglan.

06:53.510 --> 06:54.170
Therefore,

06:54.240 --> 06:55.430
even if we die in battle,

06:55.430 --> 06:56.510
we absolutely can't retreat!

06:56.510 --> 06:58.190
-You're right!
-You're right!

06:58.190 --> 06:59.680
After I escort Her Highness
back to the capital,

06:59.680 --> 07:00.950
I will return as soon as possible.

07:00.950 --> 07:01.950
During this time,

07:02.040 --> 07:02.830
all affairs

07:03.390 --> 07:04.830
will be temporarily handled by Lu Li.

07:04.830 --> 07:06.690
You must report everything to her

07:06.920 --> 07:08.070
and follow her arrangements.

07:08.070 --> 07:08.730
-Yes!
-Yes!

07:10.040 --> 07:10.720
Report!

07:11.920 --> 07:12.450
General,

07:12.600 --> 07:13.730
Her Highness is ill.

07:21.430 --> 07:22.760
She was fine yesterday.

07:23.040 --> 07:24.170
Why is she ill today?

07:30.680 --> 07:31.240
How is it?

07:32.240 --> 07:33.630
Judging by Her Highness's complexion,

07:33.630 --> 07:35.360
it seems she ate something bad.

07:35.800 --> 07:36.830
Ate something bad?

07:36.830 --> 07:38.870
Perhaps it's because,
having traveled a long way,

07:38.870 --> 07:40.070
Her Highness is weary

07:40.070 --> 07:42.680
and is unaccustomed to the climate.

07:43.560 --> 07:44.360
Have you tried the medicine?

07:44.360 --> 07:45.830
I have administered medicine,

07:45.830 --> 07:47.360
but the effect is not great.

07:47.510 --> 07:48.040
Perhaps,

07:48.270 --> 07:51.190
acupuncture can make it work faster.

07:51.870 --> 07:53.630
Then apply the needles quickly.

07:53.630 --> 07:54.390
Well...

07:54.920 --> 07:56.250
The acupuncture points

07:56.310 --> 07:58.510
are all major points on a female's body.

07:58.750 --> 08:00.010
She is a noble princess

08:00.040 --> 08:01.570
and is to marry His Majesty.

08:02.390 --> 08:04.320
It is inappropriate for me to do so.

08:05.190 --> 08:05.920
It seems

08:06.190 --> 08:07.650
we have to ask her for help.

08:19.950 --> 08:22.040
You've packed your things so quickly?

08:22.040 --> 08:22.430
Yes.

08:22.950 --> 08:24.210
I'm leaving tomorrow.

08:32.200 --> 08:33.330
Can you do me a favor?

08:33.630 --> 08:35.870
It's not time for acupuncture
until tonight.

08:35.870 --> 08:36.799
What's the rush?

08:37.600 --> 08:38.730
Her Highness is ill.

08:40.510 --> 08:41.750
We are departing tomorrow.

08:41.750 --> 08:43.280
With her in this condition,

08:43.480 --> 08:45.940
I'm afraid there will be problems
on our way.

08:55.670 --> 08:57.670
Since you took care of me yesterday,

08:58.360 --> 08:59.960
I will help you one more time.

09:02.440 --> 09:03.040
Thank you.

09:23.270 --> 09:24.130
Physician Han,

09:24.240 --> 09:26.100
how is Her Highness's condition?

09:27.150 --> 09:28.210
She is much better,

09:28.270 --> 09:30.630
but it can't be cured
in one or two sessions.

09:30.630 --> 09:32.030
Her Highness's current condition

09:32.030 --> 09:33.510
may delay our arrival in the capital.

09:33.510 --> 09:35.570
I'm afraid we can't depart tomorrow.

09:38.080 --> 09:40.540
If there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave.

09:40.910 --> 09:41.770
Physician Han.

09:41.910 --> 09:42.710
Wait a moment.

09:43.870 --> 09:44.930
Pass down my order.

09:44.960 --> 09:45.560
Tomorrow,

09:46.030 --> 09:47.430
we'll depart as planned.

09:48.150 --> 09:49.080
I'll go prepare.

09:56.150 --> 09:57.910
Why must you go to the capital?

09:58.510 --> 10:00.790
I told you, I'm going to save someone.

10:01.240 --> 10:01.910
Save whom?

10:02.510 --> 10:03.770
My second uncle's son.

10:04.080 --> 10:05.080
His name is Han Mo.

10:05.200 --> 10:07.200
He is the only male in our Han family.

10:07.670 --> 10:10.470
He is currently locked
in the capital's death row.

10:10.960 --> 10:12.360
What crime did he commit?

10:13.320 --> 10:14.240
I don't know.

10:14.870 --> 10:16.600
We lost contact many years ago.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.870
Pack up and leave tomorrow.

10:24.670 --> 10:25.720
Got it.

10:26.030 --> 10:27.750
I'll return to Changmo tomorrow.

10:27.750 --> 10:28.550
I mean,

10:29.150 --> 10:31.950
you're going back to the capital
with us tomorrow.

10:38.030 --> 10:38.870
Actually,

10:39.150 --> 10:40.510
if you give me a few more days,

10:40.510 --> 10:41.670
I can cure her.

10:42.000 --> 10:42.750
I know.

10:43.630 --> 10:45.960
That's why I said we would leave tomorrow.

10:46.270 --> 10:46.800
This way,

10:47.550 --> 10:50.010
you have a reason
to go to the capital with us.

11:16.030 --> 11:16.890
Physician Han,

11:16.910 --> 11:19.200
are you going by carriage or on horseback?

11:19.200 --> 11:20.000
On horseback.

11:20.120 --> 11:20.650
Alright.

11:21.030 --> 11:22.550
I've also prepared a carriage for you.

11:22.550 --> 11:23.720
If you get tired,

11:24.000 --> 11:25.200
you can go in and rest.

11:26.120 --> 11:27.720
General Xiao, you're very thoughtful.

11:27.720 --> 11:28.650
On this journey,

11:28.870 --> 11:30.930
I'll leave Her Highness in your care.

11:31.600 --> 11:32.330
Don't worry.

11:34.320 --> 11:34.790
Lu Li.

11:36.240 --> 11:37.040
Tianlang Pass

11:37.150 --> 11:38.280
is in your hands now.

11:38.390 --> 11:39.990
You must hold Tianlang Pass.

11:40.670 --> 11:41.390
I

11:42.030 --> 11:44.430
swear to defend Tianlang Pass
to the death.

12:19.720 --> 12:21.720
Good. Good.

12:22.240 --> 12:23.510
On such a good day,

12:23.750 --> 12:26.240
to have you,
Lord Zhang and Lord Wang, grace

12:26.270 --> 12:28.130
my humble abode is truly an honor.

12:28.150 --> 12:30.000
Come on, let's have a drink, My Lords.

12:30.000 --> 12:32.080
-Come on.
-Come on.

12:37.360 --> 12:38.240
Lord Li,

12:38.550 --> 12:40.670
the three of us
are all important officials

12:40.670 --> 12:42.930
left by the late Emperor for His Majesty.

12:43.390 --> 12:45.630
You don't need to be so polite.

12:45.630 --> 12:47.240
I'd never have known otherwise.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.630
Lord Li, your garden

12:48.750 --> 12:51.480
is even grander than His Majesty's harem.

12:52.120 --> 12:55.120
Not only are the flowers
in the courtyard beautiful,

12:55.630 --> 12:59.270
but the "flowers" on the stage
are also very alluring.

13:01.270 --> 13:04.550
Lord Zhang, you truly have great taste.

13:05.030 --> 13:06.150
These women

13:06.600 --> 13:08.660
are all dancers I bought from Changmo

13:08.790 --> 13:10.550
at a high price.

13:11.030 --> 13:14.550
Each one is highly skilled
and worth a fortune.

13:15.440 --> 13:17.550
The lead dancer, Yina,

13:17.870 --> 13:21.870
is exceptionally beautiful and priceless.

13:24.360 --> 13:27.030
These foreign dancers' performances

13:27.030 --> 13:29.440
are truly distinctive.

13:29.440 --> 13:30.910
These foreign women

13:31.030 --> 13:33.000
were originally prepared for His Majesty.

13:33.000 --> 13:34.400
But His Majesty is young,

13:34.630 --> 13:37.670
and I fear he might forsake his ambition
and neglect state affairs.

13:37.670 --> 13:38.240
However,

13:38.320 --> 13:41.120
how can we miss out on such beauty?

13:41.360 --> 13:42.390
So,

13:42.550 --> 13:43.350
I was thinking

13:43.480 --> 13:47.240
of offering these women to you, Lord Zhang

13:48.120 --> 13:49.120
and Lord Wang.

13:49.790 --> 13:52.120
Please do not decline, My Lords.

13:52.670 --> 13:53.630
Great. Great.

13:54.360 --> 13:55.000
Come on.

13:55.120 --> 13:56.910
Let's have another drink.

13:57.550 --> 13:59.360
-Come on.
-Come on.

14:02.720 --> 14:03.750
Lord Li

14:03.750 --> 14:05.750
is indeed the youngest among us.

14:06.120 --> 14:09.270
He is more far-sighted than us.

14:09.320 --> 14:10.150
Yes, right.

14:10.720 --> 14:12.790
Then, Lord Zhang,

14:13.390 --> 14:16.480
which dancer have you taken a fancy to?

14:16.840 --> 14:20.750
Good things are not about quantity,
but quality.

14:22.120 --> 14:26.510
A person should value integrity,
not greed.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.240
Understood.

14:28.630 --> 14:29.550
Later,

14:29.870 --> 14:31.730
I will send the lead dancer, Yina,

14:31.750 --> 14:34.270
to your mansion.

14:35.120 --> 14:35.750
Good.

14:38.670 --> 14:40.440
I'll send the rest of the dancers

14:40.440 --> 14:42.150
to your place, Lord Wang.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.120
Good. Good.

14:45.480 --> 14:46.480
I won't eat this.

14:47.720 --> 14:50.480
I will follow your lead, My Lords.

14:50.790 --> 14:53.790
Please guide me more.

14:56.360 --> 14:57.360
Me too.

14:57.440 --> 14:59.000
Lord Li and I

14:59.000 --> 15:00.550
also hope you, Lord Zhang,

15:00.750 --> 15:03.550
will guide us more in the future.

15:03.960 --> 15:04.670
Okay.

15:05.150 --> 15:06.550
Thanks for your trouble.

15:07.120 --> 15:10.670
On this festive day,
beauty stays by our side.

15:11.390 --> 15:13.790
Let's drink this cup together.

15:14.790 --> 15:15.360
Come on.

15:15.480 --> 15:16.240
-Come on.
-Come on.

15:16.240 --> 15:18.120
-Let's drink.
-Let's drink.

15:28.150 --> 15:28.910
What's wrong?

15:28.910 --> 15:30.310
Are you not feeling well?

15:30.750 --> 15:31.390
No.

15:31.870 --> 15:32.480
I haven't ridden a horse this long

15:32.480 --> 15:34.150
in quite some time.

15:34.720 --> 15:36.670
Do you want to rest in the carriage?

15:37.550 --> 15:38.010
No need.

15:38.390 --> 15:40.120
If you can ride a horse, so can I.

15:41.030 --> 15:41.510
Okay.

15:41.910 --> 15:42.390
Hyah!

15:52.960 --> 15:53.490
General,

15:53.630 --> 15:54.160
Lord Fei,

15:54.550 --> 15:57.010
we've carefully checked the surroundings.

15:57.440 --> 15:59.550
There is a carriage in the backyard,
but no one is in it.

15:59.550 --> 16:01.440
There is nothing else suspicious.

16:01.440 --> 16:01.960
Good.

16:02.150 --> 16:03.440
Then go settle Her Highness down first.

16:03.440 --> 16:03.840
Yes.

16:04.790 --> 16:05.320
Let's go.

16:19.320 --> 16:21.650
Is this what they deem thorough checking?

16:33.550 --> 16:35.210
Please have a seat, everyone.

16:37.550 --> 16:38.320
Please sit.

16:41.150 --> 16:42.080
Why are you here?

16:43.360 --> 16:45.670
Xiao Chi, you're escorting
Her Highness to the capital.

16:45.670 --> 16:47.790
It must be an extremely exhausting,
long journey.

16:47.790 --> 16:48.790
How could you not even

16:48.790 --> 16:50.030
get a good night's sleep?

16:50.030 --> 16:50.790
So,

16:50.790 --> 16:53.000
I've reserved this inn in advance,

16:53.150 --> 16:55.120
so Xiao Chi and Lord Fei,

16:55.120 --> 16:57.180
you can have a place to stay on the way.

16:57.480 --> 16:58.960
That's very thoughtful of you, Ms. Tang.

16:58.960 --> 16:59.890
You're welcome.

17:00.320 --> 17:01.870
The rooms are also ready.

17:02.200 --> 17:03.390
After everyone finishes eating,

17:03.390 --> 17:04.480
you can rest early.

17:06.750 --> 17:08.790
Then I won't disturb you all.

17:09.000 --> 17:09.880
I'll go to the kitchen

17:09.880 --> 17:11.540
and serve the delicious food.

17:22.640 --> 17:24.640
It seems having Ms. Tang fond of you

17:24.829 --> 17:26.000
does have its perks.

17:31.200 --> 17:31.720
Then,

17:32.160 --> 17:34.240
Physician Han, after your meal,

17:34.720 --> 17:37.250
remember to see to
Her Highness's treatment.

17:40.070 --> 17:41.030
Got it.

17:41.350 --> 17:42.440
I'll tend to

17:42.440 --> 17:43.510
both of you in turn.

17:51.790 --> 17:53.510
I checked with a silver needle before.

17:53.510 --> 17:54.640
You were poisoned.

17:54.830 --> 17:57.030
Although I don't know who poisoned you,

17:58.000 --> 17:59.600
this incident has granted me

17:59.640 --> 18:00.970
passage to the capital.

18:01.720 --> 18:02.110
Why

18:03.000 --> 18:04.600
are you going to the capital?

18:05.400 --> 18:07.060
To save my long-lost brother.

18:09.400 --> 18:11.860
Things in this world
are quite interesting.

18:12.350 --> 18:14.310
We haven't seen each other
for so many years.

18:14.310 --> 18:16.350
I wonder if he will still recognize me

18:16.350 --> 18:17.480
when we meet again.

18:19.790 --> 18:20.510
Perhaps,

18:21.270 --> 18:22.670
even if he recognizes me,

18:23.030 --> 18:25.030
he wouldn't want to acknowledge me.

18:27.550 --> 18:29.750
I don't understand what you're saying.

18:30.350 --> 18:32.030
But still, thank you, Physician Han,

18:32.030 --> 18:33.890
for treating Her Highness today.

18:34.750 --> 18:35.270
No need.

18:36.000 --> 18:37.460
By treating Her Highness,

18:37.550 --> 18:40.010
General Xiao will give me
more medical fees.

18:41.350 --> 18:42.000
Besides,

18:42.400 --> 18:44.530
treating people for free is something

18:44.680 --> 18:45.790
I've done before.

18:49.750 --> 18:50.280
Alright.

18:51.240 --> 18:53.240
How are you feeling, Your Highness?

18:53.510 --> 18:54.270
Much better.

18:55.030 --> 18:56.030
Thank you, Physician Han.

18:56.030 --> 18:57.400
After a few more acupuncture sessions,

18:57.400 --> 19:00.400
the toxins in your body
should be completely cleared.

19:01.000 --> 19:02.750
Your medical skills are excellent,

19:02.750 --> 19:03.960
and you are so dedicated.

19:03.960 --> 19:05.690
If you were by my father's side,

19:05.830 --> 19:08.510
I would beg him every day
to let you take my pulse.

19:09.510 --> 19:11.910
Then wouldn't you
have to suffer every day?

19:13.480 --> 19:14.350
Don't worry.

19:14.680 --> 19:16.510
You are so beautiful and kind.

19:16.640 --> 19:17.830
Even when you arrive in the capital,

19:17.830 --> 19:18.920
as long as you need me,

19:18.920 --> 19:20.680
you can have Jin Xi find me anytime.

19:20.680 --> 19:22.140
Thank you, Physician Han.

19:22.270 --> 19:23.680
Hearing you say this,

19:24.000 --> 19:25.330
I feel much more at ease.

19:26.750 --> 19:27.440
Then,

19:27.550 --> 19:29.150
please rest, Your Highness.

19:38.240 --> 19:39.680
I've cured Her Highness.

19:39.680 --> 19:41.030
How do you plan to thank me?

19:41.030 --> 19:41.920
You said

19:41.920 --> 19:44.320
General Xiao would reward you handsomely.

19:47.110 --> 19:47.750
However,

19:48.400 --> 19:51.000
we will still have to trouble you
along the way.

19:51.750 --> 19:52.550
How many years

19:53.240 --> 19:55.370
of my medical fees will this sum cover?

20:13.440 --> 20:14.300
Physician Han.

20:16.030 --> 20:16.790
Tonight,

20:17.920 --> 20:19.510
you're pressing a little too hard
with the needles.

20:19.510 --> 20:22.440
I've never inserted the needles
too harshly, not once.

20:22.440 --> 20:25.160
Perhaps General Xiao,
you're afraid of pain.

20:30.110 --> 20:31.640
How could I be afraid of pain?

20:31.640 --> 20:32.960
It's better if you're not.

20:32.960 --> 20:33.960
Starting today,

20:34.160 --> 20:36.030
I'll give you a massage after acupuncture.

20:36.030 --> 20:37.200
It might hurt more.

20:37.680 --> 20:39.080
You'll have to endure it.

20:41.440 --> 20:41.970
Massage?

20:44.240 --> 20:45.240
How do you do that?

20:46.030 --> 20:49.000
It means with these hands,

20:49.240 --> 20:51.590
I use varied force

20:52.110 --> 20:52.830
to press,

20:53.350 --> 20:54.110
lift,

20:54.720 --> 20:55.440
knead,

20:55.830 --> 20:56.830
and rub your body.

20:57.680 --> 20:58.590
You will

20:58.920 --> 21:00.200
place your hands on my body?

21:00.200 --> 21:00.750
Yes.

21:00.830 --> 21:03.480
Directly massage your body with my hands.

21:05.440 --> 21:05.900
Well...

21:06.110 --> 21:06.830
Why?

21:07.200 --> 21:08.800
Are you afraid I'll hurt you?

21:09.590 --> 21:10.920
That's not what I meant.

21:11.440 --> 21:12.170
It's just...

21:14.440 --> 21:15.640
I've never let a woman

21:16.070 --> 21:17.030
touch my body.

21:17.400 --> 21:19.350
I've only ever practiced
locating acupoints

21:19.350 --> 21:21.070
on wooden mannequins.

21:21.310 --> 21:23.160
It's my first time trying it
on a real person too.

21:23.160 --> 21:24.240
It's both our first time.

21:24.240 --> 21:24.830
I'm not shy.

21:24.830 --> 21:25.920
Why should you be?

21:31.720 --> 21:32.920
-I just...
-Xiao Chi!

21:33.550 --> 21:34.160
Miss Tang?

21:35.160 --> 21:36.020
Why is she here?

21:36.310 --> 21:37.310
How should I know?

21:37.590 --> 21:39.520
Ask her yourself when she comes in.

21:40.030 --> 21:41.270
She loves you so much

21:41.440 --> 21:42.920
and has taken such good care of everyone.

21:42.920 --> 21:44.070
She wants to see you.

21:44.240 --> 21:45.270
Shouldn't you hurry up and see

21:45.270 --> 21:46.440
what she wants?

21:46.830 --> 21:48.750
Well, at least wait until I get dressed.

21:48.750 --> 21:49.350
Oh.

21:49.830 --> 21:51.630
General Xiao, are you being shy?

21:52.030 --> 21:52.630
It's fine.

21:52.790 --> 21:54.110
You'll grow accustomed
to repeated meetings.

21:54.110 --> 21:55.270
It's normal to be shy the first time.

21:55.270 --> 21:56.670
You'll be fine next time.

21:59.110 --> 22:00.030
Xiao Chi.

22:00.750 --> 22:02.150
Just a moment, Miss Tang.

22:05.350 --> 22:06.030
Come in.

22:11.880 --> 22:12.510
What is it?

22:15.400 --> 22:16.030
Oh.

22:16.310 --> 22:17.830
Physician Han, you're here too.

22:17.830 --> 22:20.270
I was treating your beloved Xiao Chi.

22:21.480 --> 22:21.750
Mm.

22:22.550 --> 22:24.880
Thanks for your hard work, Physician Han.

22:25.070 --> 22:25.920
Xiao Chi,

22:26.030 --> 22:28.000
I specifically made
some ginseng soup for you.

22:28.000 --> 22:29.200
Thank you, Miss Tang.

22:29.640 --> 22:30.770
Just leave it there.

22:37.830 --> 22:39.590
Then I'll trouble you

22:39.750 --> 22:41.440
to watch Xiao Chi

22:41.590 --> 22:43.310
drink this bowl of soup.

22:47.270 --> 22:49.070
This ginseng soup is quite good.

22:49.310 --> 22:50.640
But it's a pity.

22:50.790 --> 22:53.480
Xiao Chi can only have regular food now,

22:53.590 --> 22:54.790
no medicinal tonics.

22:54.830 --> 22:55.960
I'm tired today too.

22:56.030 --> 22:57.230
I'll have it instead.

23:01.590 --> 23:03.110
The heat was a bit off.

23:03.640 --> 23:05.170
Simmer it longer next time.

23:06.200 --> 23:08.530
You drank my soup, yet you still complain.

23:08.830 --> 23:10.200
If there's nothing else,

23:10.200 --> 23:11.600
Miss Tang, you may leave.

23:18.480 --> 23:20.200
If you fail to cure Xiao Chi,

23:20.270 --> 23:22.730
be careful—
I might slip you some laxatives.

23:33.270 --> 23:34.270
She's left.

23:36.240 --> 23:36.920
So,

23:37.160 --> 23:38.750
are we still doing the massage?

23:38.750 --> 23:39.550
Of course.

23:40.590 --> 23:41.450
I was thinking,

23:41.830 --> 23:42.590
maybe

23:42.830 --> 23:43.720
you could do it over my clothes.

23:43.720 --> 23:44.650
Absolutely not.

23:45.110 --> 23:45.830
Through your clothes,

23:45.830 --> 23:48.110
I can't find the exact acupoints

23:48.550 --> 23:49.880
or control my strength.

23:51.590 --> 23:52.590
I-I just think...

23:52.590 --> 23:53.680
Stop dawdling.

23:54.480 --> 23:55.080
Lie prone.

24:28.440 --> 24:30.500
The General is going to suffer again.

24:43.350 --> 24:44.350
I'm so exhausted.

24:44.590 --> 24:46.270
It seems practicing on wooden mannequins

24:46.270 --> 24:48.600
doesn't help me control my strength well.

24:54.720 --> 24:57.120
I don't know who howled
outside last night,

24:57.160 --> 24:58.790
keeping me up all night.

25:01.440 --> 25:03.240
You look quite well.

25:03.680 --> 25:05.340
Did you sleep well last night?

25:05.440 --> 25:07.100
I slept quite well last night.

25:07.270 --> 25:09.030
I didn't hear any howling.

25:09.510 --> 25:11.240
You must have misheard, Zheng.

25:14.200 --> 25:14.920
Ms. Tang,

25:15.790 --> 25:17.310
are you here to see off General Xiao?

25:17.310 --> 25:17.880
Yes.

25:18.000 --> 25:19.060
To see off Xiao Chi,

25:19.240 --> 25:21.270
and also to see you off, Lord Fei Zheng.

25:21.270 --> 25:23.070
Then we'll meet again next time.

25:27.030 --> 25:29.960
It seems we won't have to
worry about lodgings ahead.

25:31.240 --> 25:32.920
Where is the carriage?

25:33.160 --> 25:34.400
My back aches.

25:36.110 --> 25:38.110
Then take the carriage today.

25:42.070 --> 25:42.400
No,

25:43.000 --> 25:44.330
I'd better ride a horse.

25:48.880 --> 25:49.740
Your Highness.

25:50.550 --> 25:51.410
Your Highness.

25:52.830 --> 25:53.630
Let's set off.

25:58.750 --> 25:59.280
Let's go.

26:03.310 --> 26:04.030
Tomorrow,

26:04.110 --> 26:05.570
we will reach the capital.

26:39.270 --> 26:40.270
At this speed,

26:40.880 --> 26:43.010
we can arrive in the capital tomorrow.

26:44.960 --> 26:46.490
Thinking of seeing Liu Chu,

26:47.310 --> 26:49.790
I have an indescribable feeling
in my heart.

26:51.440 --> 26:52.110
By the way,

26:52.920 --> 26:53.790
along the way,

26:54.200 --> 26:56.660
I noticed Lord Fei
looking at you strangely.

26:57.310 --> 26:59.240
Did you two know each other before?

27:00.270 --> 27:01.470
How is that possible?

27:02.030 --> 27:04.270
He is an official of Jinglan.

27:04.440 --> 27:07.040
He must have lived
in Jinglan since childhood.

27:07.350 --> 27:08.000
Moreover,

27:08.440 --> 27:09.960
for all these years, I

27:10.030 --> 27:11.430
have never left Changmo.

27:11.550 --> 27:12.790
How could I know him?

27:15.720 --> 27:17.830
Anyway, I think he's a bit weird.

27:19.240 --> 27:20.370
Don't overthink it.

27:20.880 --> 27:22.610
Let me help you get to bed early.

27:40.400 --> 27:41.260
Physician Han,

27:41.830 --> 27:42.510
I thought

27:42.720 --> 27:45.030
Her Highness required
no treatment this evening.

27:45.030 --> 27:46.000
I came to you.

27:46.350 --> 27:47.240
Me?

27:48.720 --> 27:50.920
We will arrive in the capital tomorrow.

27:51.160 --> 27:52.490
After we part this time,

27:53.350 --> 27:55.750
it'll probably be hard
for us to meet again.

27:57.790 --> 27:59.590
I want to hear you tell the truth.

28:04.550 --> 28:05.720
What truth?

28:07.960 --> 28:10.750
Are you really the Jin Xi I know?

28:23.440 --> 28:26.370
There are many people
with the same name in the world.

28:26.960 --> 28:29.160
I am definitely not the person you know.

28:29.830 --> 28:30.550
After all,

28:30.790 --> 28:32.990
I have served Her Highness since I was 5.

28:33.000 --> 28:34.600
You've got the wrong person.

28:34.680 --> 28:35.200
Fine.

28:36.440 --> 28:38.310
Then consider my efforts wasted.

28:40.790 --> 28:41.650
Physician Han.

28:46.350 --> 28:47.200
Thank you.

29:10.720 --> 29:11.550
My Lady,

29:12.160 --> 29:13.820
calling me here late at night,

29:14.310 --> 29:15.720
do you have any orders?

29:20.480 --> 29:21.480
Seeing this token

29:21.750 --> 29:23.880
is the same as beholding the King of Mo.

29:24.400 --> 29:25.510
You've recognized me?
